title: Half-Baked Contest > Score 1 Ticket to MamaBear
content:
WINNERS ANNOUNCED: CONGRATS KAGORGES & KIRILL

Check it out: http://puppyrapmobile.co/

Entrepreneurial improv at it's best!  The folks at .CO are giving away a free ticket to MamaBear to the person who comes up with the best (re: funniest) tag line for this domain: puppyrapmobile.co 

HOW IT WORKS: 1. Post your tagline in the comment section below. 2. When the contest has ended, .CO will select a winner. 3. We'll post the winner to our blog and notify via email 4.  The free ticket can be used for future events so play along if you can't attend MamaBear! *Side note: the domain above is available if you're feeling lucky!
